  entries:
  - entryId: IPHONE
    priority: 100
    keywords:
    - iphone
    - iphne
    - iphonr
    - iphone near me
    allowContainsMatch: 1
    maxEditDistance: 2
    responseText: "The iPhone is Apple\u2019s line of smartphones running the iOS
      operating system, first introduced by Steve Jobs in 2007 and now in its 17th
      generation with models like iPhone 17, 17 Pro, 17 Pro Max, and iPhone Air.\r\n\r\nWhat
      iPhone is today\r\n\r\n\u2022 Current models emphasize high-end cameras, fast
      A-series chips (such as A19/A19 Pro), OLED displays with high refresh rates,
      and deep integration with Apple\u2019s services and \u201CApple Intelligence\u201D
      AI features.\r\n\r\n\u2022 iPhones run iOS (now at iOS 26), which is tightly
      integrated with Apple\u2019s App Store, privacy features like on-device encryption,
      and services such as iCloud and Apple Pay.\r\n\r\nKey features\r\n\r\n\u2022
      Hardware: Multi-touch displays, powerful processors, advanced cameras, Face
      ID, water resistance.\r\n\r\n\u2022 Software: Regular iOS updates, access to
      millions of apps, built-in apps for messaging, browsing, email, photos, media.\r\n\r\nExample
      if you\u2019re in Malta\r\n\r\n\u2022 Apple\u2019s Malta site highlights the
      iPhone 16 family and newer models via authorized resellers.\r\n\r\n\u2022 Local
      shops such as iCentre, Scan, and other retailers in Malta sell a wide range
      of models and storage options.\r\n\r\nIf you tell me your budget and what you
      mainly use your phone for (camera, gaming, battery life, etc.), I can suggest
      specific models that fit you."
