    responseText: 'I found a match for the OfficeJet 500 on DriverFetch (v8.2.1,
      64MB). Just a heads-up: DriverFetch hosts printer drivers, rather than standalone
      apps.


      To get the right version for your computer, are you using Windows,
      Mac OS, or Linux? Let me know which one you have, and I start the download
      right away!'
